CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 1, 1958, pg. A13 reads: "Ball Committee - Some of the officers and committee chairman of the Urban League Guild got together during intermission to pose for this picture. Left to right: Mrs. Jayne Williams, Miss Gwendolyn Young, Mrs. Catherine Green, Mrs. Orlean Ricco, Mrs. Elaine Gibson, Mrs. Katharyne Irvis, and Miss Doris Handy. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of six members of Urban League Guild, from left: Jayne Lewis Williams, Gwendolyn Young, Catherine Green, Orlean Ricco, Elaine Gibson, Katharyne Irvis, and Doris Handy wearing tulle corsages with pipe cleaner figures, posed in Pittsburgh Room, Penn Sheraton Hotel
